    "scenario": "你看到朋友很沮丧，于是问他怎么了。他叹了口气说：“I am disappointed because my favorite team lost the game.” 你应该如何回应他？",
    "options": [
      "That’s too bad. But it’s just a game; you’ll get over it.",
      "I know how you feel. It’s really disappointing when your team loses. Want to talk about it?",
      "You shouldn’t be so upset about a game. That’s silly."
    ],
    "answerIdx": 1,
    "pragmaticsNote": "第二项表达共情并主动倾听，是最得体贴心的回应。第一项虽然试图安慰，但轻描淡写，可能让对方觉得情绪不被重视；第三项直接否定对方的感受，显得不礼貌且缺乏同理心。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U01-S05"
  },
