      "possessive pronouns",
      "album",
      "generation"
    ],
    "audioText": "The photo album on the coffee table is ours. It contains pictures from our childhood and our parents' marriage. The old sofa in the corner is theirs, from our grandparents' generation. We feel proud of our family traditions and respect our elders.",
    "question": "根据录音，咖啡桌上的相册属于谁？",
    "options": [
