  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U02-S01-006",
    "type": "T10",
    "typeName": "翻译输入",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U02",
    "unitTheme": "Family Relationships and Shared Belongings",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "family",
      "possessive pronouns",
      "translation",
      "B1"
    ],
    "sourceText": "这些老相册记录了我们全家的童年和婚姻，所以是我们的；邻居家的那本记录了他们几代人的故事，所以是他们的。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "These old albums record the childhood and marriage of our whole family, so they are ours; that one from the neighbours records stories of their generations, so it is theirs.",
      "These old albums hold memories of our family's childhood and marriage, so they are ours; that one belonging to the neighbours holds stories of several generations of theirs, so it is theirs.",
      "These old albums document our family's childhood and marriage, so they are ours; the neighbours' album documents the stories of their generations, so it is theirs."
    ],
    "hint": "注意：ours 和 theirs 是名词性物主代词，后面不能跟名词，单独使用即可指代前面提到的物品，避免重复名词。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U02-S01"
  },
