      "household objects",
      "there is there are",
      "listening"
    ],
    "audioText": "In my new house, there are many things. In the living room, there is a ceiling with a fan and there are beautiful curtains. In the kitchen, there is a sink and a shelf. On the shelf, there are some containers, a pot, and a pan. There is also a garage for the car. The heating system needs to be checked, and the pipes should be inspected. We have a battery for emergencies. Don't forget there is an iron in the laundry room.",
