      "too",
      "enough",
      "translation"
    ],
    "sourceText": "这件衬衫够时尚，但有点太紧了。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "This shirt is fashionable enough, but it's a bit too tight.",
      "This shirt is fashionable enough, but a bit too tight.",
      "This shirt is fashionable enough, but it's a little too tight."
    ],
    "hint": "请使用 too 和 enough 结构，注意形容词的位置。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U03-S01"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U03-S01-009",
    "type": "T12",
    "typeName": "情景回应",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U03",
    "unitTheme": "Choosing Suitable Goods at the Mall",
    "difficulty": 2,
    "tags": [
      "mall",
      "shopping",
      "clothes",
      "too enough",
      "afford",
      "brand"
    ],
    "scenario": "你在商场里看中一件某品牌的羊毛大衣。你阅读标签，发现材质是100%羊毛，款式很时尚。你试穿后觉得尺码非常合适（suitable enough），但价格超出了预算，你买不起。店员询问你的决定，你会怎么回应？",
    "options": [
      "This coat is too tight and not valuable enough. I don't want it.",
      "I think this coat is affordable enough and suitable. I'll take it directly.",
      "This coat is suitable enough and very fashionable. But it's not affordable enough for me. I can't afford it."
    ],
    "answerIdx": 2,
    "pragmaticsNote": "在表达商品不合适或不够合适时，可以使用'too + 形容词'表示'太……'，如'tight'；使用'形容词 + enough'表示'足够……'，如'suitable enough'、'affordable enough'。此外，'not 形容词 + enough'表示'不够……'，如'not affordable enough'。注意选择合适的表达来描述实际情况。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U03-S01"
  },
