    "sourceText": "与竞争对手相比，这款手机的广告宣传更注重实用性，因此它被认为更可靠，也吸引了更多消费者。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "options": [
      "Comparing to its competitors, this phone's advertising focuses more on practicality, so it is considered more reliable and attracts more consumers.",
      "Compared to its competitors, the advertising of this phone focuses on more practicality, so it is considered more reliable and attracts more consumers.",
      "Compared to its competitors, this phone's advertising focuses more on practicality, so it is considered more reliable and attracts more consumers.",
      "Compared to its competitors, this phone's advertising focuses on practicality more, so it is considered reliable and attracts many consumers."
    ],
    "answerIdx": 2,
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U03-S02"
  },
  {
