    "unit": "U03",
    "unitTheme": "Comparing Products and Advertising Influence",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "comparatives",
      "superlatives",
      "advertising",
      "consumer choices"
    ],
    "audioText": "Let me compare these two competitors. The commercial for the first product promotes it as more reliable and practical, while the ad for the second product tries to persuade consumers by following the latest trend. Many consumers are influenced by marketing. However, according to standard comparisons, the first product is less expensive and more reliable than the second.",
