  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U03-S04-008",
    "type": "T12",
    "typeName": "情景回应",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U03",
    "unitTheme": "Ordering Food and Discussing Cooking Methods",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "点餐",
      "情态动词",
      "建议",
      "必要性",
      "饮食需求"
    ],
    "scenario": "你在餐厅点餐，想询问服务员菜品是烤的还是炸的，是否辣或清淡，是否含酒精。同时你需要告诉服务员你需要避免冷冻食品和含酒精的食物，并请服务员推荐合适的菜品。",
    "options": [
      "You need to bake the fish because I have to eat healthy. You ought to make it mild. Also, you shouldn't add alcohol. Now recommend something.",
      "Excuse me, could you tell me if the fish is baked or fried? I need to avoid fried food for health reasons. Also, I have to stay away from alcohol and frozen ingredients. Should I go for the mild option, or is there something you recommend?",
      "Is the fish baked or fried? I don't want fried. I also don't want alcohol or frozen food. What do you have?"
    ],
    "answerIdx": 1,
    "pragmaticsNote": "正确选项使用了情态动词（need to, have to, should）礼貌地说明个人饮食限制并请求推荐，符合餐厅交际场景。其他选项要么语气生硬，要么错误地指导服务员。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U03-S04"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U03-S04-009",
    "type": "T10",
    "typeName": "翻译输入",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U03",
    "unitTheme": "Ordering Food and Discussing Cooking Methods",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "ordering food",
      "modal verbs",
      "advice",
      "necessity",
      "restaurant"
    ],
    "sourceText": "你好，我想点菜。我该选哪道菜？这道菜是烤的还是炸的？我想要温和不辣的。我需要避免含酒精的饮品和冷冻食品。您有什么推荐？",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "Hello, I'd like to order. Which dish should I choose? Is it baked or fried? I'd like it mild, not spicy. I need to avoid alcoholic drinks and frozen food. What do you recommend?",
      "Hi, I'd like to order. Which dish should I choose? Is it baked or fried? I want it mild. I have to avoid alcoholic beverages, and I ought to stay away from frozen food. Could you recommend something?",
      "Hello, I'd like to order. Which dish should I pick? Is it baked or fried? I'd like it mild, not spicy. I need to avoid anything alcoholic or frozen. Can you give me a recommendation?"
    ],
    "hint": "请使用情态动词 (should, ought to, have to, need to) 表达建议或需求。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U03-S04"
  },
