    "difficultyNotes": "句子包含 despite（尽管）引导的状语短语，表示转折；eventually（最终）表示时间推进。注意 despite 后需接名词或动名词。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U04-S05"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U04-S05-007",
    "type": "T10",
    "typeName": "翻译输入",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U04",
    "unitTheme": "Narrating Travel Experiences and Lessons Learned",
    "difficulty": 4,
    "tags": [
      "travel",
      "linking words",
      "despite",
      "eventually",
      "therefore",
      "volunteer",
      "historic",
      "achievement"
    ],
    "sourceText": "尽管旅途中遇到了不少挑战，我最终还是作为志愿者参与了那个历史景点的保护工作，因此我取得了很大的成就感。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "Despite the many challenges during the journey, I eventually participated as a volunteer in the conservation of that historic attraction, so I gained a great sense of achievement.",
      "Despite encountering many challenges on the trip, I eventually volunteered at that historic attraction and therefore achieved a great sense of accomplishment.",
      "Although there were many challenges during the trip, I eventually took part in the conservation of that historic attraction as a volunteer, and therefore I gained a great sense of achievement."
    ],
    "hint": "注意使用“despite”或“although”引导让步，用“eventually”表达最终结果，用“therefore”或“so”表达结果。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U04-S05"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U04-S05-008",
    "type": "T09",
    "typeName": "拼写输入",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U04",
    "unitTheme": "Narrating Travel Experiences and Lessons Learned",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "linking words",
      "travel",
      "spelling",
      "B1"
    ],
    "audioText": "请拼写表示“尽管”的英文单词。",
    "hint": "这是一个介词，表示转折关系，后面接名词或动名词。意思是“尽管”。",
    "answer": "despite",
    "commonMistakes": [
      "despight",
      "dispite",
      "despiste"
    ],
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U04-S05"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U04-S05-009",
    "type": "T12",
    "typeName": "情景回应",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U04",
    "unitTheme": "Travel, Transport, and Outdoor Activities",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "travel",
      "narrating",
      "linking words",
      "conversation"
    ],
    "scenario": "你与朋友分享上周末的徒步旅行经历。你们参观了山顶的一个历史遗迹（historic attraction），景色很美（beauty）。尽管早晨下了雨（despite），你们最终还是成功登顶（eventually）。朋友问你是否拍了照片。请选择一个最合适的回应，使用连接词使叙述连贯。",
    "options": [
      "Despite the rain, we eventually reached the summit.",
      "Meanwhile, our photographer friend took some amazing pictures of the historic attraction, and we felt a great sense of achievement.",
      "Therefore, we decided to participate in a volunteer project to protect the beauty of the mountain."
    ],
    "answerIdx": 1,
    "pragmaticsNote": "选项A使用meanwhile引出同时发生的拍照活动，并与成就感衔接，既回应了提问又丰富了叙述，语用效果最佳。选项B只是重复之前的天气情况，没有直接回答是否拍照，显得多余。选项C虽然使用therefore却转移话题到志愿者活动，不符合问题焦点。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U04-S05"
  },
