    ],
    "scenario": "你和同学聊天，他问你最近有什么进展。你想告诉他你已经完成了毕业项目，并且获得了一项数据分析的资格认证。",
    "options": [
      "I was completing my final year project and I was obtaining a qualification.",
      "I complete my final year project and I obtained a qualification in data analysis.",
      "I have completed my final year project and I have also obtained a qualification in data analysis."
    ],
    "answerIdx": 2,
    "pragmaticsNote": "使用现在完成时（have/has + 过去分词）强调动作在不久前完成，且对当前状态有直接影响，是表达已取得的成就和资格的自然方式。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U05-S01"
  },
