      "I intend to continue development my skills and have decided not to quit before I retire because I am talented and ambitious.",
      "I intend to continue developing my skills and have decided not to quit before I retire because I am talented and ambitious.",
      "I intend to continue developing my skills and have decided not to retire before I quit because I am talented and ambitious."
