      "Writing is your talent. You want to specialize in it, right?"
    ],
    "answerIdx": 1,
    "pragmaticsNote": "The first response uses 'intend to quit' to confirm the friend's plan and 'enjoy working' to remind her of her positive feelings about teaching, showing concern and consideration. This is more natural and engaging than the other options, which either give unsolicited advice or shift focus.",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U05-S04"
  },
