      "announcement",
      "workplace",
      "professional communication"
    ],
    "scenario": "你正在向未能参加周会的同事转述经理在会上的公告。经理说：'The company has revised its remote work policy.' 你应该如何正确转述？",
    "options": [
      "The manager said the company has revised its remote work policy.",
      "The manager announced that the company had revised its remote work policy.",
      "The manager told that the company had revised its remote work policy."
    ],
    "answerIdx": 1,
    "pragmaticsNote": "在转述时，通常需要将现在完成时变为过去完成时（backshift），并且'announced'比'said'更正式，适合公告场景。而'told'后必须接间接宾语（如 us、them）。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U05-S05"
  },
