    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U06-S02-006",
    "type": "T10",
    "typeName": "翻译输入",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U06",
    "unitTheme": "Media, Arts, and Entertainment",
    "difficulty": 2,
    "tags": [
      "narrative tenses",
      "translation",
      "film storytelling",
      "mystery"
    ],
    "sourceText": "之前，当我讲述悬疑故事时，制片人正在调查谋杀场景，而受害者已经预感到了危险。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "Previously, while I was telling the mystery story, the producer was investigating the murder scene, and the victim had already sensed the danger.",
      "While I was relating the suspense story, the producer investigated the murder scene; the victim had previously felt the danger.",
      "The producer was investigating the murder scene as I recounted the story; the victim had sensed the danger earlier."
    ],
    "hint": "使用过去进行时（was telling/was investigating）描述背景动作，过去完成时（had sensed）表示更早发生的动作，一般过去时（investigated/recounted）表示主要动作。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U06-S02"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U06-S02-007",
    "type": "T11",
    "typeName": "语音跟读",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U06",
    "unitTheme": "Media, Arts, and Entertainment",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
