      "过去完成时",
      "过去时"
    ],
    "audioText": "The producer had previously investigated the murder before the studio released the film.",
    "scoringDimensions": [
      "发音",
      "流利度",
      "完整度"
    ],
    "difficultyNotes": "本句包含过去完成时（had investigated）和一般过去时（released）的对比，注意'previously'的发音和过去时动词的变形。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U06-S02"
  },
