    ],
    "sourceText": "和朋友讨论这张民谣专辑时，我引用了其中一首诗的句子，它的节奏令人放松，我也感到非常放松。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "When discussing this folk album with a friend, I quoted a line from one of its poems; its rhythm is relaxing, and I feel very relaxed.",
