      "When discussing this folk album with a friend, I quoted a line from one of its poems; its rhythm is relaxing, and I felt very relaxed."
    ],
    "hint": "注意区分-ing形容词（描述事物特性）和-ed形容词（描述人的感受）。例如relaxing表示“令人放松的”，relaxed表示“感到放松的”。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U06-S03"
  },
