      "sculpture",
      "portrait",
      "exhibition",
      "relative clauses"
    ],
    "scenario": "你们参观了一个摄影和雕塑展览。朋友指着一座闪闪发亮的雕塑和一组历史肖像收藏问：\"Do you know if these works are all by the same artist?\" 你知道这些作品都是由一位擅长拍摄历史肖像和创作闪亮雕塑的艺术家完成的。",
    "options": [
      "Yes, they are all by an artist, he is known for his historic portraits and shiny sculptures.",
      "Yes, they are all by an artist which is known for his historic portraits and shiny sculptures.",
      "Yes, they are all by an artist who is known for his historic portraits and shiny sculptures."
    ],
    "answerIdx": 2,
    "pragmaticsNote": "选项A使用关系从句“who is known for his historic portraits and shiny sculptures”正确描述了艺术家。选项B错误地用关系代词“which”指代人，在英语语法中是不接受的。选项C使用了逗号直接连接两个子句，缺少关系代词或连接词，结构错误。因此A是语用最合适的回应。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U06-S04"
  },
