  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U06-S05-009",
    "type": "T10",
    "typeName": "翻译输入",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U06",
    "unitTheme": "Recommending Performances and Cultural Events",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "translation",
      "opinion phrases",
      "-ed/-ing adjectives",
      "performance recommendation"
    ],
    "sourceText": "个人而言，我认为这场表演非常迷人，既浪漫又令人放松。虽然有些场景令人害怕，但观众并没有被吓到。服装和帷幕都令人惊叹，整体娱乐非常令人满意。没有人感到失望。我强烈推荐！",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "In my opinion, this performance was fascinating, romantic, and relaxing. Although some scenes were frightening, the audience was not frightened. The costumes and curtains were amazing, and the overall entertainment was very satisfying. No one was disappointed. I highly recommend it!",
      "Personally, I think this performance is absolutely fascinating, both romantic and relaxing. Even though some parts were frightening, the audience didn't feel frightened. The costumes and curtains were magnificent, and I was very pleased with the overall entertainment. Nobody was disappointed. I strongly recommend it!",
      "I believe this performance was fascinating, romantic, and relaxing. While some scenes were frightening, the audience remained unfrightened. The costumes and curtains were fantastic, and the overall entertainment was excellent. No one felt disappointed. I would definitely recommend it!"
    ],
    "hint": "请用英语翻译这句话。注意使用表达个人观点的短语（如 personally, in my opinion, I believe）以及以 -ed 和 -ing 结尾的形容词的正确形式，例如 fascinated/fascinating, frightened/frightening, disappointed/disappointing 等。确保形容词描述的是人（-ed）还是事物（-ing）要准确。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U06-S05"
  },
