    "unitTheme": "Media, Arts, and Entertainment",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "cultural reviews",
      "media opinions",
      "listening"
    ],
    "audioText": "In my editorial for the 'Nature Views' journal, I state: 'This documentary, which represents a breakthrough, reflects a strong belief in environmental protection. I doubt that any other film has such an impact. The contrast to older works is notable, yet the similarity to other conservation films is clear. In my conclusion, I give it my full recommendation.'",
    "question": "编辑认为这部纪录片反映了什么？",
    "options": [
      "与旧作品的明显对比",
      "对环境保护的强烈信念",
      "电影制作的突破"
    ],
    "answerIdx": 1,
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U06-S06"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U06-S06-006",
    "type": "T09",
    "typeName": "拼写输入",
