  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U06-S06-008",
    "type": "T10",
    "typeName": "翻译输入",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U06",
    "unitTheme": "Cultural Reviews and Media Opinions",
    "difficulty": 4,
    "tags": [
      "editor",
      "journal",
      "cultural review",
      "relative clause",
      "opinion phrase",
      "belief",
      "doubt",
      "contrast",
      "similarity",
      "recommendation"
    ],
    "sourceText": "那位在期刊上发表了文化评论的编辑认为，这部作品反映了社会信仰并影响了大众观点，但我怀疑它是否真正代表了大众。他对比了两部作品的相似之处，并给出了他的推荐。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "The editor who published a cultural review in the journal believes that this work reflects social beliefs and influences public opinion, but I doubt whether it truly represents the public. He contrasted the similarities between the two works and gave his recommendation.",
      "The editor, who published a cultural review in the journal, believes that this work reflects social beliefs and has an impact on public opinion; however, I doubt it truly represents the public. He also compared the similarities of the two works and offered his recommendation.",
      "In my opinion, the editor who published a cultural review in the journal considers this work to reflect societal beliefs and influence the public, but I question if it accurately represents the public. He drew a contrast between the two works in terms of similarity and concluded with a recommendation."
    ],
    "hint": "翻译时注意使用关系从句（who/that）修饰“编辑”，并使用“I doubt”“In my opinion”等短语表达观点。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U06-S06"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U06-S06-009",
    "type": "T12",
    "typeName": "情景回应",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U06",
    "unitTheme": "Cultural Reviews and Media Opinions",
    "difficulty": 4,
    "tags": [
      "文化评论",
      "关系从句",
      "观点短语"
    ],
    "scenario": "你正在阅读一本艺术期刊，其中一位编辑发表了一篇文化评论。评论讨论了一部纪录片如何反映环保信念，并与另一部电影进行了对比，最后给出了推荐。你的朋友问你：“What do you think of the editor’s opinion?” 你会如何回应？",
    "options": [
      "The editor provided a detailed comparison and gave a recommendation. I think it is helpful.",
      "I doubt that the editor's reflection on the belief is accurate. The represent of the content is not clear.",
      "I believe the editor's review, which contrasts the two films effectively, is very insightful. In my opinion, his recommendation is worth considering."
    ],
    "answerIdx": 2,
    "pragmaticsNote": "正确选项使用了关系从句（which contrasts...）对评论作补充说明，并用 I believe 和 In my opinion 表达个人观点，符合作回应时的语用需求。其他选项要么缺少关系从句，要么存在语法或用词错误，语用效果不如正确选项得体。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U06-S06"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U06-S06-010",
    "type": "T11",
    "typeName": "语音跟读",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U06",
    "unitTheme": "Media, Arts, and Entertainment",
