      "adverbs of frequency",
      "environmental vocabulary",
      "translation"
    ],
    "sourceText": "核废料对大气层高度危险，煤炭资源被频繁消耗，导致全球变暖风险显著上升。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "options": [
