      "energy"
    ],
    "scenario": "你和同学正在讨论不同能源对环境的影响。同学说：“核能产生的废物非常危险，但燃煤电厂排放的二氧化碳也很严重。” 你想指出核废料的处理频率和煤炭使用的频率，并表达程度。你会怎么回应？",
    "options": [
      "Nuclear waste is highly dangerous and is rarely handled safely, while coal is frequently burned, causing fairly high emissions.",
      "Nuclear waste is slightly dangerous and is regularly handled safely, while coal is rarely burned, causing slightly low emissions.",
      "Nuclear waste is highly dangerous and is frequently handled safely, while coal is regularly burned, causing highly low emissions."
    ],
    "answerIdx": 0,
    "pragmaticsNote": "Option A correctly uses degree adverbs (highly, fairly) and frequency adverbs (rarely, frequently) that match realistic assessments of nuclear waste handling and coal combustion, maintaining coherence with the discussion.",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U09-S04"
  },
