      "natural events"
    ],
    "audioText": "First, pressure builds up beneath the Earth's surface. Then, the force is released, and an earthquake occurs. After that, the ground shakes slightly. Finally, the damage has been measured and recorded.",
    "question": "根据录音，地震发生的过程是怎样的？",
    "options": [
