  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U10-S01-001",
    "type": "T03",
    "typeName": "Matching",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U10",
    "unitTheme": "Comparing Cultural Customs and Identity",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "culture",
      "customs",
      "complex sentences",
      "matching"
    ],
    "pairs": [
      {
        "left": "Because the religion emphasizes community, the celebration includes a shared feast.",
        "right": "因为宗教强调社区，庆祝活动包括共享盛宴。"
      },
      {
        "left": "Although the bride wears a traditional dress, she also incorporates modern accessories.",
        "right": "虽然新娘穿着传统服饰，她也融入了现代配饰。"
      },
      {
        "left": "Whether the ceremony is held in a church or a temple, the priest leads the prayers.",
        "right": "无论仪式是在教堂还是寺庙举行，神父都会带领祈祷。"
      },
      {
        "left": "Historical customs differ between nations, yet each generation preserves its own identity.",
        "right": "历史习俗因国家而异，但每一代都保留着自己的认同。"
      }
    ],
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U10-S01"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U10-S01-002",
    "type": "T05",
    "typeName": "补全句子",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U10",
    "unitTheme": "Comparing Cultural Customs and Identity",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "complex-sentences",
      "cultural-comparison",
      "conjunctions"
    ],
    "sentence": "_____ the wedding ceremony in western nations often focuses on the bride and groom, traditional customs in many Asian cultures emphasize the union of two families.",
    "blank": "Although",
    "options": [
      "Although",
      "Since",
      "Because",
      "Whether"
    ],
    "answerIdx": 0,
    "hint": "表达转折关系，前后两分句对比：西方婚礼关注新人，亚洲习俗强调两个家庭的结合。用 Although 引导让步状语从句。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U10-S01"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U10-S01-003",
    "type": "T08",
    "typeName": "Listening Choice",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U10",
    "unitTheme": "Comparing Cultural Customs and Identity",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "listening",
      "culture",
      "complex sentences"
    ],
    "audioText": "Although western weddings often feature a white dress, many Asian cultures have a red bride dress because red symbolizes good luck. Whether the ceremony is religious or secular, the priest or officiant usually leads the couple to pray for happiness.",
    "question": "根据听力，哪一项描述是正确的？",
    "options": [
      "所有仪式都是宗教性的。",
      "亚洲文化中新娘穿红色婚纱，因为红色象征好运。",
      "西方婚礼通常穿红色婚纱。"
    ],
    "answerIdx": 1,
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U10-S01"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U10-S01-004",
    "type": "T06",
    "typeName": "Sentence Ordering",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U10",
    "unitTheme": "Comparing Cultural Customs and Identity",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "culture",
      "comparison",
      "complex sentences",
      "grammar",
      "vocabulary"
    ],
    "words": [
      "celebrations",
      "they",
      "Although",
      "cultural",
      "during",
      "identity.",
      "western",
      "value",
      "people",
      "religious",
      "still",
      "customs",
      "pray",
      "traditional",
      "many",
      "because",
      "from",
      "ceremonies,",
      "differ",
      "their"
    ],
    "targetSentence": "Although western customs differ from traditional ceremonies, many people still pray during religious celebrations because they value their cultural identity.",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U10-S01"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U10-S01-005",
    "type": "T07",
    "typeName": "翻译选择",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U10",
    "unitTheme": "Comparing Cultural Customs and Identity",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "complex sentences",
      "cultural customs",
      "translation"
    ],
    "sourceText": "虽然不同国家的婚礼习俗各不相同，但无论是在西方还是东方，新娘都会在仪式上祈祷，因为宗教信仰在历史上影响了这些传统。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "options": [
      "Whether wedding customs differ across nations, although in the West or the East, the bride prays during the ceremony because religious belief has historically influenced these traditions.",
      "Because wedding customs differ across nations, whether in the West or the East, the bride prays during the ceremony although religious belief has historically influenced these traditions.",
      "Although wedding customs differ across nations, whether in the West or the East, the bride prays during the ceremony because religious belief has historically influenced these traditions.",
      "Although wedding customs are similar across nations, whether in the West or the East, the bride prays during the ceremony because religious belief has historically influenced these traditions."
    ],
    "answerIdx": 2,
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U10-S01"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U10-S01-006",
    "type": "T09",
    "typeName": "Spelling Input",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U10",
    "unitTheme": "Comparing Cultural Customs and Identity",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "vocabulary",
      "spelling",
      "culture"
    ],
    "audioText": "请听单词 ceremony 的发音",
    "hint": "指一种正式的仪式或典礼，常用于婚礼、宗教活动等场合",
    "answer": "ceremony",
    "commonMistakes": [
      "ceremoney",
      "ceremoni",
      "ceremoney"
    ],
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U10-S01"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U10-S01-007",
    "type": "T10",
    "typeName": "翻译输入",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U10",
    "unitTheme": "Comparing Cultural Customs and Identity",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "complex-sentences",
      "cultural-comparison",
      "conjunctions",
      "writing"
    ],
    "sourceText": "尽管各国的历史习俗不同，人们仍然一起庆祝，因为他们共享相同的文化认同。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "Although historical customs differ among nations, people still celebrate together because they share the same cultural identity.",
      "Even though historical customs vary across nations, people still celebrate together since they share the same cultural identity.",
      "Although the historical customs of different nations are different, people still celebrate together because they share the same cultural identity."
    ],
    "hint": "使用 although/even though 引导让步状语从句，because/since 引导原因状语从句。注意主谓一致和时态。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U10-S01"
  },
