  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U10-S02-004",
    "type": "T08",
    "typeName": "听力选择",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U10",
    "unitTheme": "Expressing Opinions on Global Trends and Economy",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "discourse markers",
      "global trends",
      "economy",
      "listening"
    ],
    "audioText": "Global trade has been expanding rapidly. However, the recent financial crisis has slowed growth. Therefore, many countries are focusing on domestic production. Similarly, investment in technology has increased. In contrast, export volumes have declined in some regions. In addition, the impact on employment is significant.",
    "question": "根据听力内容，哪一项最能概括说话人的观点？",
    "options": [
      "全球贸易持续增长，没有受到金融危机影响。",
      "金融危机导致增长放缓，各国转向国内生产并加大技术投资。",
      "出口量在所有地区都大幅上升。"
    ],
    "answerIdx": 1,
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U10-S02"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U10-S02-005",
    "type": "T10",
    "typeName": "翻译输入",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U10",
    "unitTheme": "Expressing Opinions on Global Trends and Economy",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "discourse markers",
      "global economy",
      "trade",
      "writing",
      "translation"
    ],
    "sourceText": "全球经济发展迅速；因此，许多国家增加了进出口贸易。然而，金融风险依然存在。此外，投资新技术能带来长期利润。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "acceptedAnswers": [
      "The global economy is developing rapidly; therefore, many countries have increased import and export trade. However, financial risks still exist. In addition, investing in new technology brings long-term profits.",
      "The worldwide economy is growing fast; therefore, many nations have expanded imports and exports. However, financial risks remain. Furthermore, investing in new technologies yields long-term profits."
    ],
    "hint": "使用 however, therefore, in addition 等连接词连接句子，注意标点符号的使用（分号、逗号）。词汇提示：rapidly/quickly, import and export, financial risks, invest in, yield/bring profits。",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U10-S02"
  },
  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U10-S02-006",
