  {
    "id": "pair_1782569237717-B1-U10-S02-007",
    "type": "T07",
    "typeName": "Translation Choice",
    "language": "en",
    "cefr": "B1",
    "unit": "U10",
    "unitTheme": "Expressing Opinions on Global Trends and Economy",
    "difficulty": 3,
    "tags": [
      "discourse markers",
      "global economy",
      "trade",
      "translation",
      "B1"
    ],
    "sourceText": "全球贸易趋势显示出积极的发展；此外，跨境投资也在增长。然而，金融不稳定性依然存在，因此政府必须谨慎制定政策。",
    "sourceLang": "zh",
    "options": [
      "Global trade trends show positive development; similarly, cross-border investment is growing. But financial instability remains; because governments must formulate policies cautiously.",
      "Global trade trends show positive development; in addition, cross-border investment is growing. However, financial instability remains; therefore, governments must formulate policies cautiously.",
      "Global trade trends show positive development; however, cross-border investment is growing. In addition, financial instability remains; so governments must formulate policies cautiously.",
      "Global trade trends show positive development; therefore, cross-border investment is growing. In contrast, financial instability remains; thus governments must formulate policies cautiously."
    ],
    "answerIdx": 1,
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U10-S02"
  },
  {
