      "global trends",
      "economy",
      "opinion"
    ],
    "scenario": "你在一个国际经济论坛的小组讨论中，想要表达你对全球贸易趋势的看法，并用连接词组织逻辑。",
    "options": [
      "I think global trade is expanding; however, protectionist policies could slow growth. Therefore, countries should invest in diversified supply chains. In addition, digital services are becoming a larger share of exports.",
      "However, therefore, similarly, in contrast, in addition.",
      "Global trade is expanding, but I like pizza."
    ],
    "answerIdx": 0,
    "pragmaticsNote": "The correct response uses discourse markers (however, therefore, in addition) to structure a coherent opinion on trade trends. The first distractor introduces an irrelevant personal preference, breaking relevance. The second distractor merely lists markers without forming a meaningful statement.",
    "pairId": "pair_1782569237717",
    "sectionId": "pair_1782569237717/U10-S02"
  },
  {
